    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\">\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg\" width=\"1407\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553551&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553551&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1080\" data-width=\"1920\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"4a18b665-7e90-472b-a974-273bd3cc9f44\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553551&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1920&amp;height=1080 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/LamaDiffuse_Header.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553551&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1407&amp;height=791 1x\"></span><p /><p>Diffuse shading is one of the most common looks in rendering with diffuse objects often dry and unpolished such as newspaper, dirt, and rocks, and is often the base of many materials.</p><p>These objects all reflect light in a wide range of directions from the surface. This means they won't be shiny or reflective, which requires something like <a href=\"/wiki/spaces/REN27/pages/542219348/LamaConductor\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219348\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">LamaConductor</a> to add shininess and reflectivity.</p><p><br/></p><h3 id=\"LamaDiffuse-DiffuseParameters\">Diffuse Parameters</h3><p><strong>Color</strong></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Color is typically where diffuse / albedo textures or patterns are connected to create color for opaque objects.</span><br/></p></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg\" width=\"446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219790\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"528060ec-8bc7-446a-973a-6f60df1de178\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_default.001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg\" width=\"446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553550&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553550&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219814\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a0efc157-0a64-4601-9d8a-e22c21a8aa3b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553550&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_LimeTiger.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553550&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg\" width=\"446\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553373&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553373&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219811\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"91b21e93-15b5-4cbc-bace-04ca7f130c7f\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553373&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Dielectric_tint_wood.002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553373&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=446&amp;height=446 1x\"></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><br/></p><p><strong>Roughness</strong></p><p><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">Diffuse roughness is how you would simulate a powdery surface like dried clay or dust.  </span><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">When roughness is 0.0,  LamaDiffuse uses the Lambertian model to calculate the diffuse response.  </span><br/><span class=\"legacy-color-text-default\">When roughness is &gt; 0.0, the Oren Nayar model is used instead.</span></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table data-table-width=\"1800\" data-layout=\"align-start\" data-local-id=\"cb90bbde-0b47-424b-a3d4-36fbea945ed7\" class=\"confluenceTable\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219808\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"70a19bae-4af2-47ba-b76b-b065407a8ae5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0001.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219805\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"126ce59b-75cf-4804-818d-f7ac197fc301\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0002.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553372&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper i