-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0005.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"a444c49a-b1e5-4835-ad79-e9a7b3280043\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0005.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553186&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td><td class=\"confluenceTd\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg\" width=\"217\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219793\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"9ba348c2-6fa1-4741-b3ad-3c118ee8c7f4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=434&amp;height=434 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_roughness.0006.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=217&amp;height=217 1x\"></span></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><br/></p><p><strong>Normal / Bump</strong></p><p>Here is where you supply a signal, either a texture or procedural pattern, to create a bump to the surface to &quot;fake&quot; surface details like small bumps or scratches. This means an artist doesn't have to model these tedious and often repetitious parts of a model.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg\" width=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"800\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219787\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"cb56888c-95e8-425c-aa0f-6a88078fe74b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/Lama_Diffuse_normal.004.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330552962&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=800 1x\"></span><p /><hr/><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" height=\"64\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/RenderManFundamentals_logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553912&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=64&amp;height=64\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542219773/RenderManFundamentals_logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553912&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542219832\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManFundamentals_logo.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542219773\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"da654fef-829c-48c4-9536-3d01720e143c\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/RenderManFundamentals_logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553912&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=64&amp;height=64 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/542219773/RenderManFundamentals_logo.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330553912&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=64&amp;height=64 1x\"></span><br/><strong>RenderMan Fundamentals</strong></p><p><br/></p><iframe align=\"middle\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"conf-macro outpu